Поднять контейнеры:
code Bash

docker compose -f docker/docker-compose.yml up -d --build

Применить миграции:
code Bash

docker compose -f docker/docker-compose.yml exec php php bin/console doctrine:migrations:migrate -n

Запустить воркер:
code Bash

docker compose -f docker/docker-compose.yml exec php php bin/console messenger:consume import_incoming queue_vessels queue_ports queue_companies -vv


Тестил работоспособность curlом
code Bash
curl -v -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/import \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "data": {
        "vessels": [
            {"imo": "9166778", "name": "Vessel One", "flag": "Panama"}
        ],
        "ports": [
            {"code": "NLRTM", "name": "Rotterdam", "country": "Netherlands"}
        ],
        "companies": [
            {"tax_id": "DE123456789", "name": "Shipping Co"}
        ]
    }
}'



